title: Lowest Female Suicide Mortality Rate
description: In 2021, Oman recorded one of the lowest female suicide mortality rates globally, with only 0.21 deaths per 100,000 female population.

title: High Employment in Industry
description: As of 2023, 40.16% of Oman's total employment is in the industrial sector, showcasing a strong industrial workforce.

title: Rapid Population Growth
description: Oman's population grew by an impressive 6.53% in 2023, indicating a rapidly expanding populace.

title: Fast Urban Population Growth
description: In 2023, Oman's urban population growth rate was 7.27%, reflecting a swift urbanization trend.

title: High Dependence on Arab World Imports
description: In 2023, 53.13% of Oman's merchandise imports came from Arab economies, highlighting a significant reliance on regional trade partners.
